com.adobe.cq.social.srp.internal

Class AbstractSchemaMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.cq.social.srp.internal.AbstractSchemaMapper

  • public abstract class AbstractSchemaMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class maps from SoCo keys and values to those used by the common schema developed by Adobe Cloud Storage. This class is only intended to be used by Communities code.

      • toSchemaKey

        public java.lang.String toSchemaKey(java.lang.String cqKey)
        Get the schema mapping of a SoCo field. Needed to map CQ fields in a query to Solr fields, since we don't have information about the field type to be able to come up with the Solr name used when adding to index. Custom fields have Solr schema names, so if not found, assume it is a custom dynamic field.
        Parameters:
        cqKey - The CQ name of a field
        Returns:
        The Solr index name for the CQ field or the input if not mapped (dynamic field name)

      • fromSchemaKey

        public java.lang.String fromSchemaKey(java.lang.String schemaKey)
        Get the CQ mapping of a schema field. Needed to map schema key to CQ field. For facet fields etc, where we don't have a map, just a string.
        Parameters:
        schemaKey - The schema name of a field
        Returns:
        The CQ field name or the input if not mapped (dynamic field name)
